          For those getting started in volunteering through team challenges
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="column col-3 certificate">
        <img src="{{~>asset_url url='images/certificates/logos/approach.png' ~}}" class="certificate-icon img-responsive" />
        <p>
          For when you've reached 10 and 25 hours volunteering
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="column col-3 certificate">
        <img src="{{~>asset_url url='images/certificates/logos/ascent.png' ~}}" class="certificate-icon img-responsive" />
        <p>
          For when you've reached 50, 100, 200 or even 500 hours
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="column col-3 certificate">
        <img src="{{~>asset_url url='images/certificates/logos/summit.png' ~}}" class="certificate-icon img-responsive" />
